"{\"uid\": \"newzimbabwe.com-zimbabwean-athlete-isaac-mpofu-eager-to-leave-mark-at-paris-olympics\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Date: By Xinhua LONG-distance Zimbabwean runner, Isaac Mpofu, who will represent the country in marathon at the Paris 2024 Olympic Games on August 10, will do his best to bring a medal home, his coach Benson Chauke has said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 16, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.24522254921805e-16, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 203, \"end\": 209, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kris_Benson\", \"score\": 0.9918836146123785, \"rank\": 0.008182800147058657, \"text\": \"Benson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kris_Benson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kris_Benson\"}, {\"begin\": 210, \"end\": 216, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"score\": 0.9999999990354809, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chauke\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Isaac Mpofu\", \"from\": 49, \"to\": 60}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 81, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"marathon\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 136}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 140, \"to\": 146}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal home\", \"from\": 177, \"to\": 189}, {\"ngram\": \"his coach\", \"from\": 191, \"to\": 200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Chauke told Xinhua in an interview ahead of the official opening of the Games on Friday that the 35-year-old sergeant in the Zimbabwe Republic Police has gone through rigorous training since January and was raring to go.Mpofu won a bronze medal at the 2023 African Games in Ghana and also participated in the World Athletics Championships in 2019 and 2022.Mpofu, one of seven athletes making up Team Zimbabwe at the Olympics, is the only one to have qualified from home since all the others are foreign-based, Chauke said.The coach said it was everyone's dream to run at high-profile games such as the Olympics and despite the anxiety associated with such an event, Mpofu was determined to bring a medal back home.\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 228, \"end\": 234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"score\": 0.9999999990354809, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chauke\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chauke\"}, {\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.24522254921805e-16, \"text\": \"Xinhua\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xinhua_News_Agency\"}, {\"begin\": 353, \"end\": 377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Republic_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zimbabwe Republic Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Republic_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zimbabwe_Republic_Police\"}, {\"begin\": 502, \"end\": 507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"score\": 0.8836548091244818, \"rank\": 0.1316505580668739, \"text\": \"Ghana\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ghana\"}, {\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 566, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.8627674886892143